OL,3,CMPs debate removal of immunity
OL,4,Cprovision from Legacy Act
OL,6,FMPs are debating the removal of the
OL,7,Fimmunity provision from the previous
OL,8,Fgovernment's legislation to deal with
OL,9,Fthe legacy of the Northern Ireland
OL,10,FTroubles.
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland Secretary Hilary Benn
OL,13,Fwill seek support later on Wednesday
OL,14,Fin the House of Commons for a Remedial
OL,15,FOrder to remove some elements of the
OL,16,FLegacy Act.
