OL,6,FMr Benn said: "Today, I am asking the
OL,7,FHouse to endorse a Remedial Order to
OL,8,Fremove indefensible and legally
OL,9,Fdefective provisions contained in the
OL,10,Fprevious government's Legacy Act.
OL,12,F"This Remedial Order is essential to
OL,13,Frebuild the trust of communities
OL,14,Facross Northern Ireland who are
OL,15,Fopposed to the idea that the
OL,16,Fterrorists who murdered their loved
OL,17,Fones could be granted immunity from
OL,18,Fprosecution if they came forward to
OL,19,Fthe commission.
