OL,6,F"It also restores the historic right
OL,7,Fof citizens of this country to seek
OL,8,Fredress through the courts."
OL,10,FBut concerns have been raised by some
OL,11,Farmed forces and veterans communities
OL,12,Fthat the Troubles Bill will leave
OL,13,Fthose who served in Northern Ireland
OL,14,Fopen to vexatious litigation.
